summary:
Proudly Chinese Panamenian living and working  in The Netherlands for the past 10 years, 
I have a vast comprension of the Dutch culture and language. Taking advantage of my multicultural background and cultures, I  am the bridge between 3 continents: Asia, America and Europe. 

I speak Spanish as my mother tongue as well as Chinese Mandarin and Chinese Cantonese. 
 
Taking advantage of my language skills and  many years of working experience in the luxury and tourism industry. I am ready to move on into my next challenge of language coaching and culture lecturing.
